These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, coffee, 7up, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, peach, apricot, carrot
4 different pets are kept: pony, mouse, ferret, hamster
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, taxi, trike
 1. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 2. the person drinking coffee is the person eating carrot##1
 3. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 9. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Beverage    | 7up   | coffee       | water | soy-milk   |
| Food        | peach    | carrot  | apricot      | lettuce |
| Pet         | hamster      | mouse | ferret         | pony   |
| Transport   | boat | jet-ski       | taxi        | trike   |

