.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, nurse, doctor, manager
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, polish, british, pakistani
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, cricket, rugby, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, snowmobile, train, skateboard
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the nurse is the canadian##1
3. the person driving the train is the doctor##1
4. the designer is between the polish and the person driving the subway##2
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person driving the skateboard##1
7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3
9. the polish is on the left of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Job           | nurse | designer | manager | doctor |
| Nationality   | canadian  | british | polish         | pakistani      |
| Sport         | rugby      | cricket    | water-polo         | skiing   |
| Transport     | subway         | snowmobile    | skateboard          | train         |

