.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, raspberry, lemon, onion
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, jazz, techno, r&b
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, horse, fish, hamster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, water-polo, weightlifting, golf
 1. the fan of techno is the person eating lemon##1
 2. the fan of country is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
 4. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the fan of jazz##2
 9. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
10. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Food          | raspberry | onion  | cherry | lemon      |
| Music-Genre   | country       | r&b    | jazz      | techno      |
| Pet           | hamster     | rabbit     | horse         | fish   |
| Sport         | weightlifting | biathlon | water-polo     | golf |

