5. the japanese is the person watching fantasy movies##1
6. the thai is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
8. the bartender is between the owner of the mouse and the colombian##2
9. the police-officer is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
