The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, house, salsa, r&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, parkour, swimming, rowing
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
 2. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
 3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 4. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
 9. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the fan of r&b is between the person drinking 7up and the fan of salsa##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up | coffee     | water       |
| Food          | cabbage   | orange    | papaya | cauliflower       |
| Music-Genre   | indie     | house       | r&b    | salsa     |
