 1. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
 4. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating orange##2
 6. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
 8. the owner of the pony is the person driving the ship##1
 9. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | lemonade   | mirinda | sprite | hot-chocolate      |
| Food        | grapefruit | nectarine | orange   | kale     |
| Pet         | goldfish     | dog    | turtle       | pony     |
