 3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
 5. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
 6. the fan of disco is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 7. the owner of the snake is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the owner of the rabbit##2
 8. the fan of indie is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 9. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking     | baking  | traveling |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | hip-hop  | soul   | indie          |
| Pet           | hedgehog      | rabbit       | snake    | goldfish         |
