.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, asparagus, apricot, pumpkin
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, chef, writer, librarian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, action, spy, epic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, cricket, baseball, sailing
 1. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the software-developer##1
 3. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 4. the chef is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 5. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
 6. the person watching romance movies is between the chef and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
 7. the person watching spy movies is the librarian##1
 8. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person eating apricot is the chef##1
10. the person watching romance movies is the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | asparagus | pumpkin   | apricot   | tomato |
| Job           | software-developer   | writer     | chef   | librarian |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | romance    | epic   | spy   |
| Sport         | weightlifting    | cricket | sailing | baseball    |

 